# Trivy baseline — May 2026 audit HIGH-1.
#
# Format: one CVE-ID per line. Inline comments after `#` document the
# vendor advisory + expiry date. Re-evaluate on every quarterly review.
# CI fails on any CRITICAL/HIGH CVE that is NOT in this list AND has a
# fixed version available (`ignore-unfixed: true` in the workflow).
#
# Baseline starts empty. The first hard-fail run surfaces real findings;
# each gets a fix or an entry here. The README in this directory
# documents the add/remove workflow.
